IMAPStore lukaszmk1405@gmail.com-remote
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
User lukaszmk1405@gmail.com
PassCmd "cat ~/.config/isync/gmail_pw.txt"
AuthMechs LOGIN
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore lukaszmk1405@gmail.com-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path /home/lukasz/.local/share/mail/lukaszmk1405@gmail.com/
Inbox /home/lukasz/.local/share/mail/lukaszmk1405@gmail.com/INBOX

Channel lukaszmk1405@gmail.com
Expunge Both
Far :lukaszmk1405@gmail.com-remote:
Near :lukaszmk1405@gmail.com-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
SyncState *
MaxMessages 0
ExpireUnread no
# End profile

